      "content": "that makes sense. i noticed you mentioned \"neutral colors\" and \"conservative\" styles. do you have any specific examples of outfits for, say, a high-level executive meeting? and how would that look if the person is traveling to somewhere like Lagos or Mumbai vs london?",
